page.title: 10EYE BYPASS 2
page.content: The Government doesn't want the bypass to go the South route because they ill have to pay the farmers for their land, lay their own foundations and the route is longer. People who have houses next to the railway track don't want it to go the North route because the by pass will be right next to their house. My friend ,Matthew Bagster , has a gate leading out on to the railway track. If the pass is made via the North route, I don't think he will want to open his gate to a main road. The bypass might even be a Dual carriageway. So these are the arguments and questions about the bypass for{Eye.}The people of{Eye }are in suspense until August when the government will decide which way the by pass should go.
